694
00:34:28,639 --> 00:34:30,620
Eunchae, don't do this to me.

695
00:34:29,770 --> 00:34:34,570
[Sujin: Don't do this to me.]
[Hyeyeon: Eunchae, any ideas for a question?]

696
00:34:35,300 --> 00:34:39,909
[Hyeyeon: You must have a top choice and a second choice.]

697
00:34:41,780 --> 00:34:44,980
[Hyeyeon: As of tonight,]

698
00:34:44,980 --> 00:34:46,850
[Hyeyeon: what's the gender of your number one?]

699
00:34:47,120 --> 00:34:49,250
[Sujin: Oh, come on, you can ask
something way juicier than that.]

700
00:34:49,250 --> 00:34:50,850
[Hyeyeon: Oh, really? Let me take that back then.]

701
00:34:51,650 --> 00:34:55,389
[Hyeyeon: If the person you like]

702
00:34:55,389 --> 00:34:59,400
[Hyeyeon: is hitting it off with someone else,]

703
00:34:59,660 --> 00:35:02,600
[Hyeyeon: will you still pursue them?]

704
00:35:02,870 --> 00:35:04,730
[Hyeyeon: Would you get in their way?]

705
00:35:05,540 --> 00:35:08,200
[Sujin: I'd stick to them like glue.]

706
00:35:07,860 --> 00:35:08,220
Get in the way?

707
00:35:08,200 --> 00:35:12,480
[What are you doing? Was your date fun?]

708
00:35:12,740 --> 00:35:18,080
[Sujin: It sounded like she was asking
if I'd keep pursuing Heejin.]

709
00:35:18,080 --> 00:35:19,680
[Sujin: I said yes.]

710
00:35:19,680 --> 00:35:22,620
[Sujin: I wanted to make Hyeyeon]

711
00:35:22,620 --> 00:35:26,090
[Sujin: sweat a little.]

712
00:35:27,420 --> 00:35:31,160
[Who gets picked this time?]

713
00:35:31,160 --> 00:35:33,300
[Sujin: It's Heejin.]
[Jinwoo: It's Heejin.]

714
00:35:34,860 --> 00:35:37,220
[Nervous]

715
00:35:37,980 --> 00:35:40,020
[Thinking]

716
00:35:40,500 --> 00:35:45,140
[Hyeyeon: Heejin, out of everyone
you like right now,]

717
00:35:45,140 --> 00:35:51,380
[Hyeyeon: I want to know the gender
of your top choice.]

718
00:35:51,420 --> 00:35:52,980
Mmm.

719
00:35:53,260 --> 00:35:53,580
[Thinking]

720
00:35:53,580 --> 00:35:54,920
[Thinking]
[Hyeyeon: Your top choice.]

721
00:35:55,340 --> 00:35:58,580
[Sujin: Uh, isn't that question kind of tame?]
[Hyeyeon: Oh, really? Well, we're roommates.]

722
00:35:58,580 --> 00:35:59,720
[Sujin: That's tamer than I expected.]

723
00:36:02,390 --> 00:36:04,260
[Heejin: It's a girl.]

724
00:36:04,380 --> 00:36:06,500
[Smile]

725
00:36:07,020 --> 00:36:08,900
[Smile]

726
00:36:14,940 --> 00:36:16,010
[Eunchae: These 2 haven't been picked yet, right?]

727
00:36:15,970 --> 00:36:17,310
-Right. -Not even once.

728
00:36:16,010 --> 00:36:17,870
[Seungho: Not even once.]
[Jinwoo: Not at all.]

729
00:36:17,870 --> 00:36:19,210
[Hyeyeon: Give it a good spin this time.]

730
00:36:18,750 --> 00:36:19,480
Spin it hard?

731
00:36:21,880 --> 00:36:23,480
[Sujin: Why does it keep landing over here?!]

732
00:36:23,060 --> 00:36:24,100
-But… -Exactly!

733
00:36:24,280 --> 00:36:26,680
[Hyeyeon gets picked again]

734
00:36:24,930 --> 00:36:25,640
It's your date!

735
00:36:25,640 --> 00:36:26,580
Spin again, spin again!

736
00:36:26,580 --> 00:36:27,270
Spin it hard.

737
00:36:27,270 --> 00:36:28,970
Fill up a glass first.

738
00:36:30,420 --> 00:36:32,820
[Seungho: We're asking Hyeyeon this time, right?]

739
00:36:31,260 --> 00:36:32,170
-Yeah. -Right.

740
00:36:32,860 --> 00:36:35,500
[Thinking]

741
00:36:35,780 --> 00:36:38,160
[Seungho: We had to choose date partners today, right?]

742
00:36:38,160 --> 00:36:41,360
[Seungho: But we were restricted
to the opposite gender.]

743
00:36:41,360 --> 00:36:43,230
[Seungho: If that rule didn't exist,
would you still have picked me?]

744
00:36:45,900 --> 00:36:48,300
[Seungho: If you could pick anyone,
would I still be your choice?]

745
00:36:48,300 --> 00:36:50,440
[Sujin: She's gotta drink for that.]
[Chaebe: Whoa.]

746
00:36:50,440 --> 00:36:53,380
[Chaebe: Good question.]
[Jinwoo: Right. Good one.]

747
00:36:54,710 --> 00:36:56,310
[Sujin: Take a shot!]

748
00:36:56,310 --> 00:36:57,650
[Sujin: Are you going to drink instead?]

749
00:36:58,180 --> 00:37:00,850
[Hyeyeon: Oh, absolutely! I would.]

750
00:37:04,620 --> 00:37:06,380
[Whoa, that's so cool.]

751
00:37:06,480 --> 00:37:07,360
Seriously.

752
00:37:07,790 --> 00:37:09,590
-So cool. -Let me spin this time.

753
00:37:10,990 --> 00:37:14,460
[Seungho: I asked a pretty bold question.]

754
00:37:14,460 --> 00:37:16,070
[Seungho: I thought she'd just drink to pass,]

755
00:37:16,070 --> 00:37:17,400
[Seungho: but she actually said "yes."]

756
00:37:17,400 --> 00:37:19,540
[Seungho: It made me really happy.]

757
00:37:20,340 --> 00:37:22,470
[Jinwoo: Honestly,
I didn't want to hear any more.]

758
00:37:22,470 --> 00:37:25,140
[Jinwoo: I felt so anxious and insecure.]

759
00:37:25,140 --> 00:37:28,340
[Jinwoo: I couldn't help feeling jealous.]

760
00:37:28,340 --> 00:37:29,680
[Jinwoo: It was really frustrating.]

761
00:37:30,480 --> 00:37:34,480
[The atmosphere gets intense
as the truth game goes on]

762
00:37:36,350 --> 00:37:37,690
[Sujin: Let's swap seats.]

763
00:37:37,690 --> 00:37:39,560
[Hyeyeon: Grab your own glass.]

764
00:37:40,360 --> 00:37:42,020
[Eunchae: Go ahead and swap;
I'm heading to the bathroom.]

765
00:37:42,020 --> 00:37:44,630
[Chaebe: Me too.]
[Heejin: Same here.]

766
00:37:44,160 --> 00:37:45,160
Go ahead if you need to.

767
00:37:45,160 --> 00:37:46,290
Time for a quick break.

768
00:37:46,290 --> 00:37:47,550
Break time.

769
00:37:46,660 --> 00:37:48,340
[Break Time.]

770
00:37:47,550 --> 00:37:48,530
Hurry back. 5 minutes!

771
00:37:48,420 --> 00:37:51,300
[Yongkyu: Going out for a smoke?]
[Jinwoo: Let's go out.]

772
00:37:52,640 --> 00:37:54,500
[Hyeyeon: Aren't you going?]
[Sujin: Nope.]

773
00:37:54,450 --> 00:37:55,920
-Drink some water. -Okay.

774
00:37:54,500 --> 00:37:56,640
[Hyeyeon: Have some water.]

775
00:37:56,700 --> 00:37:57,710
Me too.

776
00:38:01,180 --> 00:38:03,580
[Sujin: This is pretty fun, right?]
[Hyeyeon: Yeah.]

777
00:38:04,110 --> 00:38:05,450
[Sujin: I just thought of a question.]

778
00:38:05,450 --> 00:38:07,320
[Hyeyeon: What is it? Just between us?]

779
00:38:08,120 --> 00:38:10,790
[Sujin: Your first impression vote
and your second vote—]

780
00:38:10,790 --> 00:38:13,720
[Mmm.]
[Sujin: were they the same or different?]

781
00:38:13,720 --> 00:38:16,390
[Hyeyeon: I picked different people.]

782
00:38:16,390 --> 00:38:19,600
[Sujin: Really?]
[Hyeyeon: Yeah, I voted for someone different.]

783
00:38:20,220 --> 00:38:22,800
[Hyeyeon: What about you?]
[Sujin: I voted for the same person.]

784
00:38:25,900 --> 00:38:27,540
[Hyeyeon: That's when I realized
I completely misread the situation.]

785
00:38:27,540 --> 00:38:31,070
[Hyeyeon: I got zero votes.]

786
00:38:31,070 --> 00:38:33,480
[Hyeyeon: I was so sure that Sujin]

787
00:38:33,480 --> 00:38:36,150
[Hyeyeon: liked me.]

788
00:38:36,150 --> 00:38:38,810
[Hyeyeon: Oh... I had it all wrong.]

789
00:38:38,810 --> 00:38:41,750
[Hyeyeon: In that split second,
I realized she wasn't into me.]

790
00:38:42,820 --> 00:38:46,140
[Hyeyeon grows more and more confused]

791
00:38:46,140 --> 00:38:47,460
[Hyeyeon: Let's start over, shall we?]

792
00:38:46,270 --> 00:38:47,460
-Let's... -Start over.

793
00:38:47,460 --> 00:38:48,500
[Sujin: The two of us
were talking about an interesting question.]

794
00:38:48,690 --> 00:38:49,860
[Sujin: What is it?]

795
00:38:49,860 --> 00:38:52,160
[Hyeyeon: We should all answer this.]
[Sujin: Yeah, everyone should answer.]

796
00:38:52,160 --> 00:38:55,900
[Sujin: The question is,
did you vote for the same person]

797
00:38:55,900 --> 00:38:59,100
[Sujin: on day one]

798
00:38:59,100 --> 00:39:02,040
[Sujin: as you did today?]

799
00:39:03,370 --> 00:39:05,240
[Sujin: Eunchae?]
[Eunchae: Ah, everyone?]

800
00:39:05,240 --> 00:39:06,580
[Sujin: Yeah, everyone answers.]

801
00:39:06,580 --> 00:39:08,180
[Eunchae: Different.]

802
00:39:09,250 --> 00:39:10,580
[Sujin: Same.]

803
00:39:11,110 --> 00:39:12,980
[Hyeyeon: Different.]

804
00:39:13,520 --> 00:39:15,920
[Seungho: Same.]

805
00:39:15,920 --> 00:39:16,450
[Sujin: Heejin?]

806
00:39:16,450 --> 00:39:17,790
[Heejin: Different.]

807
00:39:18,320 --> 00:39:19,390
[Chaebe: Different, too.]

808
00:39:19,390 --> 00:39:20,990
[Jinwoo: Same.]

809
00:39:20,990 --> 00:39:22,590
[Yongkyu: Same, too.]

810
00:39:23,660 --> 00:39:27,130
[Everyone shares how they voted]

811
00:39:27,660 --> 00:39:31,130
[Everyone's feelings are starting to become clear]

812
00:39:31,670 --> 00:39:35,140
[Hyeyeon: How about we start
with Yongkyu and go around, asking each person]

813
00:39:35,140 --> 00:39:37,270
[Hyeyeon: whatever you'd like to ask?]
[Heejin: So we can ask anyone we want?]

814
00:39:37,270 --> 00:39:38,340
[Hyeyeon: Yeah, we'll just go in that order,]

815
00:39:38,340 --> 00:39:39,940
[Hyeyeon: and end with Eunchae.]

816
00:39:40,480 --> 00:39:42,350
[Hyeyeon: Let's do the final round,
starting with Yongkyu.]

817
00:39:42,350 --> 00:39:44,750
[Hyeyeon: Final round, starting with Yongkyu.]

818
00:39:45,010 --> 00:39:46,380
[Heejin: Has anyone asked you this yet?]

819
00:39:46,380 --> 00:39:48,020
[Heejin: Tomorrow,]

820
00:39:48,020 --> 00:39:50,460
[Heejin: will you choose a guy or a girl
for your date?
Has anyone asked it?]

821
00:39:53,820 --> 00:39:55,960
[Yongkyu: Same gender.]

822
00:39:55,960 --> 00:39:57,830
[Heejin: Go on. Next.]

823
00:39:57,830 --> 00:39:58,890
[Jinwoo: Next.]

824
00:39:59,700 --> 00:40:03,970
[Hyeyeon: Even if the person
you like most right now]

825
00:40:03,970 --> 00:40:07,440
[Hyeyeon: is falling for someone else,]

826
00:40:07,700 --> 00:40:10,640
[Hyeyeon: will you keep fighting to win them over?]

827
00:40:12,240 --> 00:40:14,910
[Hyeyeon: The penalty shots are ready.]

828
00:40:13,840 --> 00:40:14,580
3 shots.

829
00:40:14,910 --> 00:40:17,580
[Jinwoo: I'd keep going after them.]

830
00:40:18,380 --> 00:40:20,780
[Sujin: So loyal.]

831
00:40:22,090 --> 00:40:22,820
Impressive.

832
00:40:22,920 --> 00:40:24,340
[Jinwoo: Any other questions?]

833
00:40:24,790 --> 00:40:26,660
[Yongkyu: Do you remember
what Chaebe's first question was?]

834
00:40:26,660 --> 00:40:27,990
[What was Chaebe's first  question?]

835
00:40:27,990 --> 00:40:29,590
[Sujin: He didn't get to ask one, right?]

836
00:40:29,590 --> 00:40:31,990
[Sujin: Did Chaebe ask someone else a question?]

837
00:40:31,990 --> 00:40:35,200
[Yongkyu: He only asked others;
he hasn't answered anything himself.]

838
00:40:32,190 --> 00:40:33,120
Wait, Chaebe...

839
00:40:35,200 --> 00:40:37,870
[Yongkyu: Ah, well...]

840
00:40:36,550 --> 00:40:37,680
-Exactly. -Well...

841
00:40:38,670 --> 00:40:41,600
[Yongkyu: Does the person you voted
for the first time]

842
00:40:41,600 --> 00:40:42,940
[Yongkyu: live in the main building
or the annex?]

843
00:40:42,940 --> 00:40:44,010
[Chaebe: The first one?]

844
00:40:44,010 --> 00:40:45,880
[Yongkyu: The person you voted for.]

845
00:40:45,880 --> 00:40:46,940
[Chaebe: They live in the main building.]

846
00:40:47,580 --> 00:40:48,740
[Sujin: What about the second time?]

847
00:40:48,740 --> 00:40:50,540
[Chaebe: I have to answer both?]

848
00:40:50,540 --> 00:40:53,880
[Hyeyeon: Well,
since you haven't answered any questions.]

849
00:40:55,100 --> 00:40:58,020
[Chaebe: For the second one,
they live in the annex.]

850
00:40:58,020 --> 00:40:59,420
[Jinwoo: I have a question.]

851
00:40:58,030 --> 00:40:58,880
What is it?

852
00:40:59,420 --> 00:41:01,980
[Jinwoo: If you could go on a date,]

853
00:41:01,980 --> 00:41:06,700
[Jinwoo: would you prefer a guy or a girl?]

854
00:41:07,380 --> 00:41:10,170
[Chaebe: I'd prefer a guy.]

855
00:41:10,340 --> 00:41:11,060
A man.

856
00:41:12,840 --> 00:41:14,220
[Seungho: I'm curious about something.]

857
00:41:14,220 --> 00:41:18,710
[Seungho: Your roommates right now...]

858
00:41:18,940 --> 00:41:21,110
[Seungho: Is the person you voted
for today one of them?]

859
00:41:21,540 --> 00:41:25,380
[Hyeyeon: That narrows it down way too much!]
[Sujin: That's... that's...]

860
00:41:22,330 --> 00:41:24,280
-That's... that's… -That is savage.

861
00:41:24,280 --> 00:41:26,540
-Well, nothing you can do. -Drink the penalty shot!

862
00:41:25,380 --> 00:41:26,450
[Sujin: Drink up! Take the shot!]

863
00:41:27,780 --> 00:41:30,190
[Chaebe: Wait, guys, think about it.]

864
00:41:30,190 --> 00:41:32,860
[Chaebe: If I just drink, it looks even guiltier!]

865
00:41:32,860 --> 00:41:37,390
[Hyeyeon: Come on, I drank
whenever my answers were vague too.]

866
00:41:36,410 --> 00:41:37,760
-So... -Really?

867
00:41:37,390 --> 00:41:39,800
[Yongkyu: Just give him a shot. Just one.]

868
00:41:37,760 --> 00:41:39,690
-Just give him a shot. -Because...

869
00:41:40,260 --> 00:41:43,530
[Yongkyu: Just give him one shot.
He can't hold his liquor.]

870
00:41:43,940 --> 00:41:45,500
[Yes!]

871
00:41:44,980 --> 00:41:45,880
A full shot then.

872
00:41:45,700 --> 00:41:47,260
[Oh?]

873
00:41:47,500 --> 00:41:49,180
[Gasps!]

874
00:41:50,300 --> 00:41:51,830
Oh my god.

875
00:41:51,020 --> 00:41:53,700
[Blushing]

876
00:41:52,480 --> 00:41:54,680
-He answered! -This is so interesting.

877
00:41:56,860 --> 00:41:57,720
Damn.

878
00:41:58,380 --> 00:42:00,040
Let's wrap it up here. Next...

879
00:42:02,220 --> 00:42:03,550
[Chaebe: I decided to say it.]

880
00:42:03,820 --> 00:42:05,420
[Chaebe: "Is it a roommate?"]

881
00:42:05,420 --> 00:42:07,020
[Chaebe: "Yes."]

882
00:42:07,020 --> 00:42:11,290
[Chaebe: I answered with total confidence.]

883
00:42:11,560 --> 00:42:18,230
[How does Yongkyu feel
hearing Chaebe's shy confession?]

884
00:42:20,370 --> 00:42:24,640
[Chaebe: If you successfully couple up at the end,]
[Heejin: Yeah.]

885
00:42:25,710 --> 00:42:28,910
[Chaebe: which gender would you rather end up with?]

886
00:42:28,910 --> 00:42:30,510
[Heejin: Doesn't matter to me.]

887
00:42:30,510 --> 00:42:32,180
[Sujin: Well, based on right now,]

888
00:42:32,180 --> 00:42:33,340
[Sujin: would you pick a guy]

889
00:42:33,340 --> 00:42:35,180
[Sujin: or a girl?]

890
00:42:34,470 --> 00:42:35,720
Right, right now. Your real feelings.

891
00:42:35,180 --> 00:42:37,450
[Sujin: Right at this exact moment.]

892
00:42:35,720 --> 00:42:36,650
Yeah, right now.

893
00:42:37,120 --> 00:42:38,320
At this exact second.

894
00:42:38,790 --> 00:42:40,920
[Heejin: A girl.]

895
00:42:41,720 --> 00:42:45,730
[Hyeyeon: You just said your first
and second votes went to different people.]

896
00:42:44,820 --> 00:42:45,550
Right.

897
00:42:46,000 --> 00:42:49,730
[Hyeyeon: So have you completely moved on]

898
00:42:49,730 --> 00:42:53,740
[Hyeyeon: from the person]

899
00:42:53,740 --> 00:42:56,140
[Hyeyeon: you first voted for?]

900
00:42:56,410 --> 00:43:00,140
[Hyeyeon: Is that why you switched your vote
to someone else?]

901
00:43:03,080 --> 00:43:05,210
[Heejin: I can answer that.]

902
00:43:05,210 --> 00:43:07,080
[Heejin: But are you seriously asking
because you don't know?]

903
00:43:08,900 --> 00:43:10,860
[Curious...]

904
00:43:13,220 --> 00:43:16,690
[Heejin: No, I haven't moved on.]

905
00:43:16,690 --> 00:43:21,230
[Hyeyeon: Then how would you
split your feelings between the two?]

906
00:43:24,430 --> 00:43:26,300
[Heejin: 70-30.]

907
00:43:26,300 --> 00:43:29,770
[Hyeyeon: Is the first person 70 or 30?]

908
00:43:26,390 --> 00:43:27,920
-The first is 70 -Yeah.

909
00:43:27,920 --> 00:43:29,220
or 30?

910
00:43:29,770 --> 00:43:32,440
[Heejin: Judging by her questions,]

911
00:43:32,440 --> 00:43:34,840
[Heejin: she really cared about the fact]

912
00:43:34,840 --> 00:43:37,250
[Heejin: that I didn't vote for her on day 2.]

913
00:43:37,780 --> 00:43:41,250
[Heejin: My mind kind of went blank for a second.]

914
00:43:42,850 --> 00:43:44,190
[Seungho: Anyone got a question for me?]

915
00:43:44,190 --> 00:43:45,790
[Jinwoo: I do.]

916
00:43:48,990 --> 00:43:52,460
[Jinwoo: When you make your final choice,
if you switch your pick,]

917
00:43:52,460 --> 00:43:54,330
[Jinwoo: will it be because]

918
00:43:54,330 --> 00:43:58,600
[Jinwoo: you've lost feelings
for the person you've always chosen,]

919
00:43:58,600 --> 00:44:01,700
[Jinwoo: or because you developed
feelings for someone new?]

920
00:44:01,690 --> 00:44:02,650
-If… -What do you mean?

921
00:44:01,900 --> 00:44:02,660
[What do you mean?]

922
00:44:02,700 --> 00:44:05,270
[Jinwoo: If you choose someone else...]

923
00:44:06,610 --> 00:44:09,550
[Sujin: If Seungho chooses someone else,]

924
00:44:10,350 --> 00:44:13,550
[Jinwoo: does it mean he's completely
over his previous pick]

925
00:44:13,550 --> 00:44:17,820
[Jinwoo: and moving on?]
[Sujin: Or is it just because he wants
to try someone new?]

926
00:44:19,690 --> 00:44:23,960
[Seungho: I couldn't decide
whether to take the shot or answer.]

927
00:44:23,960 --> 00:44:26,100
[Seungho: I was torn over it for a long time.]

928
00:44:26,100 --> 00:44:32,500
[Seungho: It's a 60-40 split
between Jinwoo and Hyeyeon. The gap isn't that big.]

929
00:44:34,640 --> 00:44:38,110
[Seungho falls silent,
struggling to give an easy answer]

930
00:44:38,950 --> 00:44:39,900
Cheers.

931
00:44:40,510 --> 00:44:43,710
[Hyeyeon and Jinwoo wait for Seungho's answer]

932
00:44:44,060 --> 00:44:45,060
Have a gummy bear.

933
00:44:46,180 --> 00:44:48,220
[Seungho: Can I just drink?]

934
00:44:48,220 --> 00:44:48,780
[Pauses]

935
00:44:50,320 --> 00:44:51,390
Your hand is literally shaking.

936
00:44:51,390 --> 00:44:52,260
It's fine.

937
00:44:51,450 --> 00:44:54,660
[Seungho dodges the question]

938
00:44:55,270 --> 00:44:56,670
Are you sure you're okay?

939
00:44:59,460 --> 00:45:02,670
[Hyeyeon: Our date didn't win me any points.]

940
00:45:02,670 --> 00:45:06,670
[Hyeyeon: Realizing that made me feel a bit down.]

941
00:45:08,800 --> 00:45:10,410
[Jinwoo: First off, I could clearly feel]

942
00:45:10,410 --> 00:45:13,340
[Jinwoo: that Hyeyeon also
had feelings for Seungho.]

943
00:45:13,340 --> 00:45:14,680
[Jinwoo: The reality finally hit me.]

944
00:45:14,680 --> 00:45:17,880
[Jinwoo: The whole scene felt so ridiculous,
like a cheap drama.]

945
00:45:17,880 --> 00:45:20,280
[Jinwoo: I couldn't help but wonder,]

946
00:45:20,280 --> 00:45:21,880
[Jinwoo: "What on earth should I do now?"]

947
00:45:22,780 --> 00:45:27,220
[They get a clear picture of
where everyone stands through the truth game]

948
00:45:33,100 --> 00:45:36,570
[Hyeyeon tidies up her vanity]

949
00:45:36,830 --> 00:45:38,430
[Heejin: You okay?]

950
00:45:38,430 --> 00:45:39,770
[Heejin: How did you drink so much?]

951
00:45:40,300 --> 00:45:43,510
[Hyeyeon: Everyone's questions were just so brutal.]

952
00:45:43,940 --> 00:45:45,140
[Looks around]

953
00:45:45,180 --> 00:45:48,040
[Heejin checks if anyone is around]

954
00:45:45,990 --> 00:45:47,290
Cleaning up quickly.

955
00:45:48,840 --> 00:45:50,710
[Heejin: I think you overdid it tonight.]

956
00:45:50,710 --> 00:45:54,450
[Hyeyeon: Luckily, I can hold my liquor pretty well.]

957
00:45:54,450 --> 00:45:58,190
[Hyeyeon: I feel a bit buzzed,]

958
00:45:58,190 --> 00:45:59,520
[Hyeyeon: but I'm definitely not wasted.]

959
00:45:59,520 --> 00:46:00,860
[Heejin: You sure you're good?]
[Yep.]

960
00:46:01,260 --> 00:46:05,590
They targeted me with way too many questions.

961
00:46:07,020 --> 00:46:11,620
[Heejin: Didn't you join my chat room today?]

962
00:46:11,620 --> 00:46:14,260
[What?]
[Heejin: Didn't you join my chat room today?]

963
00:46:14,260 --> 00:46:16,070
[Hyeyeon: Your room?]

964
00:46:15,070 --> 00:46:15,740
Yeah.

965
00:46:16,610 --> 00:46:20,080
[Heejin: You didn't join]

966
00:46:20,080 --> 00:46:21,140
[Heejin: my anonymous chat room?]

967
00:46:24,610 --> 00:46:29,150
[Hyeyeon: Well, you and I already
talked a lot, like, way earlier.]

968
00:46:29,170 --> 00:46:31,650
We talked a lot back in the first episode.

969
00:46:31,550 --> 00:46:33,690
[Heejin: Make sense.]
[Hyeyeon: I already knew everything about you anyway.]

970
00:46:33,690 --> 00:46:37,960
[Hyeyeon: So I decided to check out]

971
00:46:37,960 --> 00:46:40,360
[Hyeyeon: the other rooms instead.]

972
00:46:40,360 --> 00:46:42,500
[Heejin: Ah, I see.]

973
00:46:43,030 --> 00:46:44,820
[Heejin: But I actually joined yours today, you know?]

974
00:46:45,620 --> 00:46:47,300
[Awkward]

975
00:46:48,510 --> 00:47:06,590
-My room? -Yeah, I knew it was yours and joined.

976
00:46:48,660 --> 00:46:50,240
[Heejin: I knew it was yours and joined.]

977
00:46:51,310 --> 00:46:53,710
[Hyeyeon: This is so embarrassing.
I can't even keep talking to you.]

978
00:46:53,710 --> 00:46:55,140
[Heejin: "Too embarrassed to keep talking"?]

979
00:46:55,140 --> 00:46:56,020
[Yeah.]
[Heejin: "Too embarrassed to keep talking"?]

980
00:46:56,060 --> 00:46:58,140
[Heejin: Come on. You're usually
so good with words.]

981
00:46:58,220 --> 00:46:59,850
[Hyeyeon: The alcohol is hitting me now.]

982
00:46:59,850 --> 00:47:03,050
[Heejin: I fall for this exact trick every single time.]

983
00:47:03,050 --> 00:47:05,190
[Hyeyeon: My head is spinning a bit.]

984
00:47:06,590 --> 00:47:08,410
-I don't know what to do. -Such a liar.

985
00:47:06,790 --> 00:47:09,990
[Heejin: Such a liar.]
[Hyeyeon: Hey, I literally just downed 3 shots.]

986
00:47:11,590 --> 00:47:12,660
[Heejin: Fair enough.]

987
00:47:12,660 --> 00:47:14,000
[Hyeyeon: Go get washed up first.]

988
00:47:14,000 --> 00:47:15,600
[Heejin: I'm super fast, you know.]

989
00:47:15,600 --> 00:47:18,800
[Hyeyeon: I'll wait for you right here then.]

990
00:47:18,800 --> 00:47:20,670
[Hyeyeon: Like a good girl.]

991
00:47:20,670 --> 00:47:22,000
[Heejin: No. Seeing you like this,]

992
00:47:22,000 --> 00:47:24,940
[Heejin: I don't think you're gonna wait for me.]

993
00:47:23,470 --> 00:47:25,000
I'll wait for you like this.

994
00:47:27,980 --> 00:47:32,940
[Yongkyu sneaks in a workout before washing up]

995
00:47:39,620 --> 00:47:41,140
[Turns head]

996
00:47:41,620 --> 00:47:44,700
[Yongkyu: Good work today.]
[Chaebe: You too.]

997
00:47:47,180 --> 00:47:49,380
[Passing each other]

998
00:47:51,700 --> 00:47:55,370
[Chaebe seems to be avoiding Yongkyu]

999
00:47:55,640 --> 00:47:57,100
[Chaebe: Things got so awkward.]

1000
00:47:57,100 --> 00:48:01,340
[Chaebe: The questions thrown at me
were just way too intense.]

1001
00:48:01,620 --> 00:48:04,420
[Chaebe: But honestly, I don't regret it.]

1002
00:48:04,420 --> 00:48:08,380
[Chaebe: But I felt a bit uncomfortable,
so I kept some distance.]

1003
00:48:08,380 --> 00:48:10,980
[Chaebe: To avoid Yongkyu...]

1004
00:48:10,980 --> 00:48:14,590
[Chaebe: I even stepped out of the room
and wandered around outside...]

1005
00:48:15,620 --> 00:48:19,060
[Chaebe: Later, I lay down on the bed first.]

1006
00:48:20,200 --> 00:48:22,100
[Yongkyu's footsteps are heard outside]

1007
00:48:22,140 --> 00:48:22,980
[Hiding]

1008
00:48:23,020 --> 00:48:26,070
[Chaebe: So I covered my face with a pillow.]

1009
00:48:30,700 --> 00:48:33,340
[Yongkyu: What time are you getting up tomorrow? ]
[Chaebe: Ah, you scared me.]

1010
00:48:34,140 --> 00:48:37,280
[Yongkyu: What time are you getting up tomorrow?]
[Chaebe: Eight.]

1011
00:48:36,200 --> 00:48:37,670
-Eight? -Same as always.

1012
00:48:37,940 --> 00:48:41,780
[Chaebe: But Yongkyu still talked
to me naturally.]

1013
00:48:41,780 --> 00:48:45,300
[Chaebe: I was actually thankful
to Yongkyu for that.]

1014
00:48:45,820 --> 00:48:47,820
[After the truth game ends, a subtly awkward
atmosphere fills BI-LIVE]

1015
00:48:47,820 --> 00:48:50,360
[Heejin: It feels like several days have passed.]

1016
00:48:50,840 --> 00:48:52,440
[Jinwoo: I feel like I've been here
about four days.]

1017
00:48:52,440 --> 00:48:54,780
[Heejin: Yeah, me too.]

1018
00:48:54,780 --> 00:48:57,520
[Jinwoo: Both mentally and physically...]

1019
00:48:58,180 --> 00:48:59,920
[Jinwoo: My emotions have been all over the place
in just one day.]

1020
00:48:59,920 --> 00:49:03,120
[Jinwoo: And the situation keeps changing.]

1021
00:49:03,120 --> 00:49:05,520
[Heejin: But I experienced quite a few
surprising things today.]

1022
00:49:05,520 --> 00:49:07,340
[Jinwoo: When?]

1023
00:49:07,340 --> 00:49:10,060
[Heejin: During the truth game...]

1024
00:49:08,800 --> 00:49:10,060
Ah, during the truth game.

1025
00:49:10,060 --> 00:49:11,530
[Jinwoo: Was it confusing?]

1026
00:49:11,530 --> 00:49:13,000
[Heejin: I didn't know who picked me
today, and also...]

1027
00:49:13,270 --> 00:49:14,870
[Jinwoo: I was sure it was Eunchae.]

1028
00:49:14,870 --> 00:49:17,270
[Jinwoo: Since I went on a date
with Eunchae today...]

1029
00:49:17,270 --> 00:49:21,010
[Jinwoo: As she was talking about
her ideal type, I was listening...]

1030
00:49:21,010 --> 00:49:23,410
[Jinwoo: And suddenly (Heejin's) face
popped into my head.]

1031
00:49:22,570 --> 00:49:23,670
-Really? -It kept lingering in my mind.

1032
00:49:23,410 --> 00:49:25,810
[Heejin: But I honestly didn't
expect that at all.]

1033
00:49:25,810 --> 00:49:28,210
[Heejin: The funniest thing though...]

1034
00:49:28,210 --> 00:49:31,420
[Heejin: We had that private chat today, right?]

1035
00:49:31,420 --> 00:49:33,550
[Heejin: At the time, I thought (the people in the
private chat) were just them.]

1036
00:49:33,550 --> 00:49:35,690
[Heejin: But as the truth game went on...]

1037
00:49:35,690 --> 00:49:38,620
[Heejin: The more I played, the more
it didn't add up.]

1038
00:49:38,190 --> 00:49:38,860
So...

1039
00:49:38,620 --> 00:49:41,560
[Heejin: Huh? Something must be off.]

1040
00:49:43,160 --> 00:49:46,900
[Hyeyeon comes out after washing up]

1041
00:49:47,260 --> 00:49:48,780
[Sneaking a glance]

1042
00:49:48,820 --> 00:49:52,240
[Heejin: That person could be lying too.]

1043
00:49:51,990 --> 00:49:53,800
-What? -Could be a liar.

1044
00:49:52,240 --> 00:49:53,940
[Heejin: Could be a liar.]

1045
00:49:53,940 --> 00:49:54,700
[Seungho: You mean Hyeyeon?]

1046
00:49:54,700 --> 00:49:54,910
[Right]
[Seungho: You mean Hyeyeon?]

1047
00:49:54,910 --> 00:49:57,310
[Right]
[Jinwoo: Ah, what she said today?]

1048
00:49:58,220 --> 00:50:00,250
[Jinwoo: Was she throwing us off?]

1049
00:50:00,900 --> 00:50:04,780
[Heejin: When I talked to Hyeyeon...]

1050
00:50:04,780 --> 00:50:07,720
[Heejin: I felt like she had a pretty
good impression of me.]

1051
00:50:07,720 --> 00:50:09,320
[Heejin: But during the truth game, Sujin said...]

1052
00:50:09,320 --> 00:50:14,390
[Heejin: Hyeyeon picked the same person on
day one and day two.]

1053
00:50:14,390 --> 00:50:18,400
[Heejin: I thought she picked me today.]

1054
00:50:18,400 --> 00:50:21,870
[Heejin: So I thought, "I knew it.
I wasn't overthinking it."]

1055
00:50:21,870 --> 00:50:24,540
[Heejin: But it turned out Hyeyeon picked
the same person on day one too.]

1056
00:50:24,540 --> 00:50:26,940
[Heejin: And on day one, Hyeyeon picked Sujin.]

1057
00:50:27,210 --> 00:50:30,140
[Heejin: My heart sank right then.]

1058
00:50:30,410 --> 00:50:32,280
[Heejin: So I thought I should ask clearly.]

1059
00:50:33,350 --> 00:50:37,080
[Heejin: On day one, did you pick
a guy or a girl?]

1060
00:50:37,080 --> 00:50:38,420
[Hyeyeon: Day one?]

1061
00:50:38,420 --> 00:50:40,820
[Hyeyeon: I picked...]

1062
00:50:40,820 --> 00:50:41,890
[Hyeyeon: I picked... a girl...]

1063
00:50:41,890 --> 00:50:44,820
[Heejin: You picked a girl?]
[Hyeyeon: Yeah.]

1064
00:50:44,820 --> 00:50:47,490
[Hyeyeon: Weren't we supposed to pick the person
with the strongest first impression?]

1065
00:50:47,490 --> 00:50:49,360
[Hyeyeon: Ah, I got it wrong.]

1066
00:50:49,360 --> 00:50:53,100
[Hyeyeon: They said to pick the person
with the strongest first impression,]

1067
00:50:53,100 --> 00:50:54,830
[Hyeyeon: so I took it literally and picked]

1068
00:50:54,830 --> 00:50:56,570
[Hyeyeon: the person with the strongest
first impression.]

1069
00:50:58,560 --> 00:50:59,820
I'm telling the truth.

1070
00:51:00,840 --> 00:51:03,240
[Heejin: You didn't pick me on day one, did you?]

1071
00:51:05,110 --> 00:51:09,110
[Hyeyeon: I guess I'll have to sleep
in the hallway.]

1072
00:51:10,720 --> 00:51:12,580
[Jinwoo: What do you mean? Why?]

1073
00:51:12,580 --> 00:51:15,520
[Hyeyeon: Ah, I think that's better.]

1074
00:51:16,320 --> 00:51:17,920
[Heejin: Hyeyeon got flustered right away.]

1075
00:51:17,920 --> 00:51:19,520
[Heejin: It felt like I hit the nail on the head?]

1076
00:51:19,520 --> 00:51:21,390
[Heejin: She said she has feelings
for someone else,]

1077
00:51:21,390 --> 00:51:24,330
[Heejin: but ended up picking the person with
the strongest first impression.]

1078
00:51:24,330 --> 00:51:26,200
[Heejin: But when I heard that]

1079
00:51:26,200 --> 00:51:28,600
[Heejin: I thought, "What is she even doing?"]

1080
00:51:28,600 --> 00:51:30,470
[Heejin: I felt like I lost all interest
right then.]

1081
00:51:30,740 --> 00:51:32,340
[Heejin: Like a light suddenly went out.]

1082
00:51:32,870 --> 00:51:37,740
[Emotions continue to swirl in BI-LIVE
until early morning]

1083
00:51:38,740 --> 00:51:43,550
[After a chaotic night, day three morning arrives]

1084
00:51:43,820 --> 00:51:47,820
[Who's the first to wake up in the quiet BI-LIVE?]

1085
00:51:58,760 --> 00:52:03,840
[Sujin: Heejin said she's a light sleeper
because of the lamp light.]

1086
00:52:03,840 --> 00:52:07,570
[Sujin: She told me she didn't sleep well.]

1087
00:52:07,570 --> 00:52:11,310
[Sujin: I happened to have some disposable
warm eye masks with me.]

1088
00:52:11,310 --> 00:52:13,450
[Sujin: So I gave her two.]

1089
00:52:13,450 --> 00:52:17,180
[Sujin: Hm? I wonder if they worked?
I'm curious too.]

1090
00:52:17,450 --> 00:52:21,990
[Starting the day with Heejin on her mind]

1091
00:52:22,520 --> 00:52:26,530
[In the four-person room, Heejin
is the first to wake up]

1092
00:52:29,190 --> 00:52:32,400
[Heejin: Did you sleep well?]

1093
00:52:32,400 --> 00:52:35,330
[Heejin: Why are you up so early?]

1094
00:52:37,200 --> 00:52:44,940
[Heejin: You're up? Today I got up on my own
without anyone calling me.]

1095
00:52:45,480 --> 00:52:48,410
[Heejin: I wasn't particularly upset...]

1096
00:52:48,410 --> 00:52:52,420
[Heejin: I just lost interest all at once,
so I completely let it go.]

1097
00:52:52,420 --> 00:52:55,090
[Heejin: After that, we got along
fine like roommates.]

1098
00:52:56,960 --> 00:52:59,620
[Hyeyeon: I already went on a date yesterday...]

1099
00:52:59,620 --> 00:53:03,090
[Hyeyeon: So if I get the chance today,
I'd like to go]

1100
00:53:03,090 --> 00:53:06,300
[Hyeyeon: on a date with Sujin.]

1101
00:53:06,830 --> 00:53:10,570
[Complicated emotions between the three]

1102
00:53:16,710 --> 00:53:18,580
[Heejin: Did you sleep well?]
[Jinwoo: Yeah, did you?]

1103
00:53:18,580 --> 00:53:23,920
[Heejin: Yeah, really well.]
[Jinwoo: Good. I fell asleep pretty quickly too.]

1104
00:53:19,860 --> 00:53:21,190
-Really? -That's good.

1105
00:53:28,190 --> 00:53:31,390
[Jinwoo: Since it's the day after
the truth game.]

1106
00:53:31,390 --> 00:53:33,260
[Jinwoo: I felt a lot lighter.]

1107
00:53:33,260 --> 00:53:35,130
[Jinwoo: So I had a relaxed morning.]

1108
00:53:35,130 --> 00:53:37,800
[Jinwoo: My feelings for Seungho...]

1109
00:53:37,800 --> 00:53:40,470
[Jinwoo: I'd more or less expressed them.]

1110
00:53:41,270 --> 00:53:44,740
[Jinwoo: So I woke up in a good mood too.]

1111
00:53:45,800 --> 00:53:50,340
[The four-person room is busy getting ready]

1112
00:53:51,680 --> 00:53:56,480
[Seungho is still asleep]

1113
00:53:57,550 --> 00:54:02,090
[The three-person room is also busy
as morning arrives]

1114
00:54:02,090 --> 00:54:04,760
[Yongkyu: I'm slowly getting closer to friends]

1115
00:54:04,760 --> 00:54:06,630
[Yongkyu: I hadn't talked to much before.]

1116
00:54:06,630 --> 00:54:09,030
[Yongkyu: And the weather's nice today too.]

1117
00:54:09,030 --> 00:54:11,700
[Yongkyu: I still want to go out on a date.]

1118
00:54:12,500 --> 00:54:18,100
[Eunchae: Since it's the first morning after
we got closer last night.]

1119
00:54:18,100 --> 00:54:23,180
[Eunchae: I feel like we'll be able to get along
more comfortably today.]

1120
00:54:23,180 --> 00:54:25,840
[Eunchae: So I'm looking forward to today.]

1121
00:54:26,910 --> 00:54:31,450
[After learning about Chaebe's feelings through
last night's truth game]

1122
00:54:32,420 --> 00:54:35,300
[Staring]

1123
00:54:41,060 --> 00:54:44,530
[This is so pressuring]

1124
00:54:44,530 --> 00:54:47,470
[I only stole a few glances]

1125
00:54:49,600 --> 00:54:52,800
[Chaebe: Are you going to put on makeup?]
[Yongkyu: No, I'm all set.]

1126
00:54:52,800 --> 00:54:55,470
[Chaebe: What's wrong?]
[Yongkyu: I'm all set.]

1127
00:54:55,820 --> 00:55:00,280
[An awkward atmosphere between the two men]

1128
00:55:00,810 --> 00:55:04,020
[Chaebe: Rather than getting closer...]

1129
00:55:04,020 --> 00:55:09,350
[Chaebe: I've been feeling uncomfortable
because of what happened yesterday.]

1130
00:55:09,350 --> 00:55:12,020
[Chaebe: Especially with Yongkyu.]

1131
00:55:12,020 --> 00:55:15,760
[Chaebe: I kept feeling uneasy.]

1132
00:55:15,760 --> 00:55:22,700
[Chaebe: So I deliberately kept
a bit of distance from him.]

1133
00:55:25,100 --> 00:55:27,770
[Chaebe: Sujin, what are you doing?]

1134
00:55:27,770 --> 00:55:30,580
[Sujin: I'm putting on makeup! You can come in.]

1135
00:55:32,040 --> 00:55:34,180
[Chaebe: I came because I was bored.]
[Sujin: Are you done with your makeup?]

1136
00:55:33,260 --> 00:55:33,900
Yeah.

1137
00:55:34,180 --> 00:55:38,450
[Sujin: I'm so jealous.]
[Chaebe: I finished really quickly.]

1138
00:55:37,700 --> 00:55:38,560
I'm so jealous.

1139
00:55:38,450 --> 00:55:41,920
[Sujin: Did you have fun yesterday?
Because I thought]

1140
00:55:41,920 --> 00:55:46,190
[Sujin: I have to keep asking questions
to make it interesting.]

1141
00:55:46,190 --> 00:55:50,200
[Sujin: But you...]
[Chaebe: I never got picked. I was surprised too.]

1142
00:55:47,930 --> 00:55:48,970
How could you not get picked?

1143
00:55:48,970 --> 00:55:50,020
I was surprised too.

1144
00:55:50,020 --> 00:55:52,680
-And even...  -I thought for sure I'd get picked.

1145
00:55:50,200 --> 00:55:54,470
[Sujin: And even Hyeyeon and I deliberately]

1146
00:55:54,470 --> 00:55:57,400
[Sujin: swapped seats with Chaebe and Yongkyu.]

1147
00:55:57,400 --> 00:56:00,340
[Sujin: And after we swapped, the two of us...]

1148
00:55:58,580 --> 00:55:59,980
-The two of us... -Right?

1149
00:56:00,340 --> 00:56:05,410
[Sujin: How come Chaebe just never got picked?]

1150
00:56:03,730 --> 00:56:05,050
Right? But still...

1151
00:56:05,410 --> 00:56:09,680
[Chaebe: Anyway, we got to ask what we wanted.]
[Sujin: But our questions were really intense.]

1152
00:56:09,680 --> 00:56:11,280
[Chaebe: Way too intense.]

1153
00:56:10,410 --> 00:56:11,270
Us to Chaebe...

1154
00:56:11,280 --> 00:56:14,220
[Chaebe: It was pretty much an open declaration.]
[Sujin: No, no.]

1155
00:56:14,510 --> 00:56:16,060
What do you mean "open"? Why, why?

1156
00:56:15,290 --> 00:56:20,360
[Was last night an opportunity for Chaebe?]

1157
00:56:16,060 --> 00:56:16,720
Why do you think that?

1158
00:56:16,720 --> 00:56:17,380
It's like it's out in the open.

1159
00:56:17,380 --> 00:56:19,510
Why do you think that? Why?

1160
00:56:20,690 --> 00:56:22,100
It's already out there.

1161
00:56:24,260 --> 00:56:28,180
[Pat pat]

1162
00:56:28,180 --> 00:56:31,700
[Bang bang]

1163
00:56:31,740 --> 00:56:33,390
[Hyeyeon: Do you have to hit that hard?]

1164
00:56:33,390 --> 00:56:35,040
[Jinwoo: Why are you hitting so hard
all of a sudden?]

1165
00:56:35,040 --> 00:56:37,980
[Seungho: It sticks better this way.]

1166
00:56:36,650 --> 00:56:37,530
Really?

1167
00:56:37,980 --> 00:56:41,450
[Jinwoo: Where did you see that?]

1168
00:56:42,250 --> 00:56:44,920
[Heejin is focusing on her makeup alone]

1169
00:56:46,520 --> 00:56:49,990
[Seungho: Today should still be
a 1:1 date, right?]

1170
00:56:49,990 --> 00:56:52,390
[Hyeyeon: Probably. It's like that every day.]

1171
00:56:52,390 --> 00:56:55,990
[Hyeyeon: But today shouldn't be
in order of priority, right?]

1172
00:56:55,990 --> 00:56:59,600
[Jinwoo: What do you think it'll be then?]

1173
00:56:59,600 --> 00:57:05,200
[Hyeyeon: A real game to decide? Directly?
Calling someone out?]

1174
00:57:06,270 --> 00:57:11,880
[Hyeyeon: You come out! My fists are calling you.]
[Jinwoo: Come out!]

1175
00:57:14,810 --> 00:57:17,220
[Seungho: Are you from that era?]

1176
00:57:17,220 --> 00:57:19,080
[Jinwoo: Ah, not that era.]

1177
00:57:17,220 --> 00:57:18,970
-Ah, not that era. -No.

1178
00:57:19,080 --> 00:57:20,950
[Seungho: I just know about it too.]

1179
00:57:19,860 --> 00:57:20,800
-Right. -Same here.

1180
00:57:20,800 --> 00:57:21,740
-We've only heard about it. -Exactly.

1181
00:57:20,950 --> 00:57:23,620
[Hyeyeon: We've only heard about it.]
[Jinwoo: I only know it through the media.]

1182
00:57:23,620 --> 00:57:26,560
[Jinwoo: I've never seen it live.]
[Hyeyeon: I've never seen the original either.]

1183
00:57:26,560 --> 00:57:27,630
[Jinwoo: I definitely haven't seen the original.]

1184
00:57:27,630 --> 00:57:28,690
[Hyeyeon: I don't know either.]

1185
00:57:28,690 --> 00:57:31,100
[Jinwoo: This is so awkward.]

1186
00:57:31,630 --> 00:57:33,500
[Hyeyeon: Suddenly both of them started
denying it like crazy.]

1187
00:57:33,500 --> 00:57:35,230
[Hyeyeon: Really, I haven't～]

1188
00:57:35,230 --> 00:57:36,970
[Jinwoo: But saying that makes
it even more embarrassing.]

1189
00:57:36,970 --> 00:57:39,900
[Hyeyeon: Ah, is that embarrassing?
But I really haven't, so it's fine.]

1190
00:57:39,900 --> 00:57:42,840
[Jinwoo: I mean, not knowing
is what's embarrassing.]

1191
00:57:43,380 --> 00:57:45,510
[Jinwoo: Why do you keep trying
to distance yourself?]

1192
00:57:45,510 --> 00:57:49,780
[Hyeyeon: Me? I'm not distancing myself.
I was never in it to begin with.]

1193
00:57:49,780 --> 00:57:51,650
[Jinwoo: You weren't in it from the start?]

1194
00:57:50,570 --> 00:57:51,430
Right, we're not from the same circle.

1195
00:57:51,430 --> 00:57:52,300
I'm going crazy, seriously.

1196
00:57:51,650 --> 00:57:53,520
[Hyeyeon: Right. We're not from the same circle.
Not the same circle.]

1197
00:57:53,520 --> 00:57:55,920
[Hyeyeon: You saw it yesterday, right? I kept
getting called the younger group?]

1198
00:57:55,920 --> 00:57:59,920
[Hyeyeon: Even I barely made it into
the younger group.]

1199
00:57:59,920 --> 00:58:02,190
[Seungho: I'm number one, but I'm not
that happy about it.]

1200
00:58:02,190 --> 00:58:04,460
[Hyeyeon: Why?]

1201
00:58:04,460 --> 00:58:08,730
[Jinwoo: He said he doesn't like looking young.]
[Hyeyeon: Ah, really?]

1202
00:58:04,580 --> 00:58:05,310
He said he doesn't like looking young.

1203
00:58:05,310 --> 00:58:06,110
That's right.

1204
00:58:06,930 --> 00:58:07,840
Always being treated like a kid.

1205
00:58:07,840 --> 00:58:08,750
He said it during the show too.

1206
00:58:08,730 --> 00:58:10,860
[Seungho: Always being treated like a kid.
What do I do?]

1207
00:58:10,860 --> 00:58:13,000
[Seungho: So if people are not into me,
what do I do?]

1208
00:58:13,000 --> 00:58:17,810
[Jinwoo: But kid is kid. What else can they be?]
[Seungho: You mean I'm not a kid?]

1209
00:58:17,810 --> 00:58:19,680
[Jinwoo: Oh, really?]

1210
00:58:19,680 --> 00:58:21,550
[Hyeyeon: You're grown-up who finished
a whole bottle of wine.]

1211
00:58:21,550 --> 00:58:25,280
[Jinwoo: Finishing a whole bottle of wine
makes you a grown-up. Not a kid. A grown-up.]

1212
00:58:25,280 --> 00:58:28,080
[Seungho: I downed three shots of soju yesterday.]

1213
00:58:28,080 --> 00:58:30,890
[Jinwoo: Right? Wow, you're definitely
a grown-up.]

1214
00:58:37,300 --> 00:58:39,700
[Ready, ready～]

1215
00:58:40,760 --> 00:58:42,130
Good morning.

1216
00:58:41,300 --> 00:58:45,570
[The members gather in the living room]

1217
00:58:44,240 --> 00:58:45,500
I'm the only one wearing sweatpants.

1218
00:58:45,500 --> 00:58:46,820
-We're both wearing them today. -Grey ones.

1219
00:58:46,370 --> 00:58:50,640
[What kind of date awaits them today?]

1220
00:58:46,820 --> 00:58:47,700
Right?

1221
00:58:48,060 --> 00:58:50,330
What's going on? Why are we wearing
the same thing?

1222
00:58:50,330 --> 00:58:51,790
They're exactly the same.

1223
00:58:56,250 --> 00:59:02,250
[The YES or NO date begins]

1224
00:59:02,250 --> 00:59:08,260
[Do you want to initiate a date? (YES) or wait for
someone to ask you out? (NO)]

1225
00:59:08,260 --> 00:59:11,300
[Sujin: Alright, let me stretch my fingers first.]

1226
00:59:11,580 --> 00:59:13,380
[Thinking hard]

1227
00:59:13,380 --> 00:59:16,800
[Jinwoo: You have to think about this one too.]
[Sujin: It's a mind game, huh? Alright.]

1228
00:59:15,240 --> 00:59:16,440
A mind game. Alright.

1229
00:59:16,800 --> 00:59:19,740
[Yongkyu: Being fast with your hands
is actually a disadvantage.]

1230
00:59:16,830 --> 00:59:18,440
-Being fast is a disadvantage. -Disadvantage.

1231
00:59:18,440 --> 00:59:19,590
Who's the mafia?

1232
00:59:20,270 --> 00:59:24,010
[The members stand at a crossroads
with YES or NO]

1233
00:59:24,540 --> 00:59:28,280
[What choices will they make for their own love?]
